== Tiskanin timuta ==
[[Tugna:Sun - August 1, 2010.jpg|250px|thumb|Tugna s yiniten isaflawen tettwasseknew s [[anegjenjaṛ|unegjenjaṛ]] tesskanay-d affaw seg telmest C (tama tamellalt deg wamur azelmaṭ afellay)]] 

Tafukt d itri yeṭṭafaren talmest n [[alkam agejdan|welkam agejdan G]], [[Takura|Takura-ines]] tessiliɣ-d azal n 99.8632% seg tkura n [[Udus anafuk|wudus anafuk]] ma d talɣa-ines cki-tt d tuzza (meḥsub d tamduṛant) anda akdu deg tizgelt d win yemgaraden ɣef ukdu deg usebges s 10 km kan. Mya tafukt tga deg [[addaden n tnegwa|waddad]] n [[plasma (tasengama)|plasma]] anecta yennumk d akken-it tetezzi s urured deg [[asebges|usebges]] ugar n wayen i d-ttezzi deg tzeglin, dɣa tikeli ayi tettwassen s [[Tuzzya n tfukt|tuzzya tamgirdant]], anecta igellu-d s [[Taseddimt|tseddimt]] d unwiwel n tkura s usrag n wuẓeẓ meqqren deg [[taẓɣelt|teẓɣelt]] seg weɣyay ɣer beṛṛa. Takura ayi tettaddam kra seg [[imir amussay|yimir amussay]].<ref> Michael Zellik (2002). Astronomy: The Evolving Universe (9th ed.). Cambridge University Press. p. 240. ISBN 978-0-521-80090-7. OCLC 223304585.</ref>

Tallit tufrint n tuzzya n tfukt tettaṭṭaf 25,6 n wussan deg usebges-is d 33,5 n wussan deg tzeglin-is. Ma d tallit n tuzzya tamaskadt deg usebges teṭṭafaf 28 n wussa.<ref name=Phillips1995-78>Phillips, 1995, pp. 78–79</ref><br/>Asemdu n [[tadusi tuẓẓlammast|tdusi tuẓẓlammast]] n tuzzya ayi talwayant tga 18 n imelyan n tikkal ddaw n [[tadusi n teldayt|tdusi n teldayt]] tajummant deg usebges. Yerna [[tadusi n tndeffert]] n yimtiwgen d tis ur nli ara (ur nesɛi ar) asemdu meqqren, ɣef wanect-a ur ssemduyen ara ɣef tfukt.<ref name=Schutz2003>{{Tanagit s wedlis|aneggar=Schutz|amezwar=Bernard F.|azwel=Gravity from the ground up|aseggas=2003|anefsar=Cambridge University Press|uṭṭun ameslugen=9780521455060|tasniwin=98–99}}</ref>

== Tafat n tfukt ==
[[Tugna:Gas giants and the Sun (1 px = 1000 km).jpg|thumb|250x250px|Imtiwgen igazawen icafcalen n tfukt: [[Yebter]], [[Awihad]], [[Uṛanus]] yakk d [[Niftun]] (ibelɣen s yimsektayen imassaɣen)]] 

[[Tafat]] n tfukt d aɣbalu agejdan n [[Tafasa|tfasa]] deg [[tagnit|tegnit]] ma d iɣbula niden gan d tinegwa tisinsinin deg wuln tegnit, dɣa tinegwa ayi tisinsinin gant d aɣbalu [[Tarakaẓɣalt|tarakaẓɣalt n tegnit]] i d-ittilin s tsedmirin tiɣisanin.<br/>
[[Timezgit tanafukt]] d tasmekta n tfasa i d-ttak tfukt i wfimidi n tigget n tjumma yettwafsaren srid i tafat n tfukt.<ref> Bargagli1، R.؛ Catenil، D.؛ Nellil، L.؛ Olmastronil، S.؛ Zagarese، B. (August 1997)، "Environmental Impact of Trace Element Emissions from Geothermal Power Plants"، Environmental Contamination Toxicology، New York: Springer، 33 (2): 172–181، ISSN 0090-4341، doi:10.1007/s002449900239</ref>, Timezgit tanafukt n tjumma ɣef wuggug n [[tigget tasnullant]] yegda uggug n tegnit ɣef tfukt (azal n 1368 wat/m)<sup>2</sup><ref name=TSI>{{Tanagit s web|Azwel=Construction of a Composite Total Solar Irradiance (TSI) Time Series from 1978 to present |akala=https://www.pmodwrc.ch/pmod.php?topic=tsi/composite/SolarConstant|Azemz n tuwwṭa = 2005-10-05| akala n ufaylu = https://web.archive.org/web/20180113070251/http://www.pmodwrc.ch:80/pmod.php?topic=tsi/composite/SolarConstant | Azemz n ufaylu = 13 yennayer 2018 }}</ref>
[[Tignewt titriklant|Tignut n tegnit]] d tin yettekkayen deg [[asifes|usifes]] n tafat n tfukt s wakka ad tili tfasa i d-ittawaṭen seg tfukt tudes ɣer 1000 wat/m<sup>2</sup> deg tegnatin tigamanin neɣ mi ara ad tili tfukt deg tdeɣra n [[ameddu|umeddu]].<ref name=El-Sharkawi2005>{{Tanagit s wedlis|aneggar=El-Sharkawi|amezwar=Mohamed A.|Azwel=Electric energy|aseggas=2005|anafsar=CRC Press|uṭṭun ameslugen=978-0-8493-3078-0|tasniwin=87–88}}</ref>
